But this age-control night cream which we use everyday, has helped with the deepest levels and really does brighten up the skin well.

Q: How does the product work for you and how has it improved your confidence?

I use this product every night, as I believe by using it every day, it has given the deepest level of treatment because for 20 minutes it just works. It has a mix of Zinc oxide, Phytosterols & plant fibres, which I believe helps protect and soothe the skin.

Before using this product, my skin was really dull. My friends would suggest I use a lighter foundation because of my facial problems. Most of the time, whenever someone asked me what I use, I would say, it doesn’t work, and that I didn’t really know what to use. I tried many products, shells that really have had no effect on my skin, like my mother’s creams.

Probably less than three months ago I had no clue what was good or bad, or what smells good, feels good. My skin was really flaky, the roughness doesn’t go and I still have acne, black spots from pimples. But now since using these products, I am much happier and that never goes.
